	<h4 id="concept">Concept</h4>
	<p>SSWL is a searchable database that allows users to discover which properties (morphological, syntactic, and semantic) 
	characterize a language, as well as how these properties relate across languages. This system is designed to be free to 
	the public and open-ended. Anyone can use the database to perform queries.</p>
